#Linux Virtual Machine Scanning Tool

This tool automates information gathering, port scanning, and privilege escalation analysis tasks on Linux systems.
Its use is recommended to check for bugs and vulnerabilities in our Linux machines. 

##  Requirements

-Linux Operating System
-Python 3.x
-Superuser privileges to run certain parts of the tool

## Installation 

To install the project you must follow these steps:

1.- git clone <Repository_url>
2.- cd <Directory_name>
3.- run main.py to start the tool

And we will have the tool installed and ready to run. The reports will be obtained in the tool's own directory and a new directory will be generated with all of them.
